name: Mahogany Bracelet
description:
'Mahogany' is a beautiful little bracelet. Shell, wood, silver and clear brown beads are tied together on a deep brown nylon cord and closed with a lobster clasp. The bracelet is 18 centimeters long, an average size. If you want it to be a little longer or shorter, feel free to ask.

All the bracelets are made by hand, so the beads can be a little differently placed from the example in the pictures.
